goals.active: Debrief Pact survivors to discover the location of Trahearne and Destiny's Edge.
goals.complete: I surveyed the area surrounding the fleet wreckage and debriefed several of the Pact survivors. They provided information about where the Mordrem Guard are taking high-value prisoners, and they steered me toward a village of friendly hylek who can aid me in my search for Trahearne and Destiny's Edge.
